commit.message:
Fix compatibility with the `--enable-string-literal` Ruby option

Ref: https://bugs.ruby-lang.org/issues/20205

This allow users to turn on frozen string literal if they so chose
and make the gem compatible with future version sof Ruby for when
frozen string literals may become the default.
